unsee]]-speaking subgroups, formerly Long Island and southeastern New York<ref name=g72>Goddard 72</ref>\n***[[Canarsie people|Canarsie]] ([[Canarsee]]), formerly Long Island New York<ref name=g72g237>Goddard 72 and 237</ref>\n***[[Esopus people|Esopus]], formerly New York,<ref name=g72/> later Ontario and Wisconsin\n***[[Hackensack people|Hackensack]], formerly New York<ref name=g72/>\n***[[Haverstraw people|Haverstraw]] ([[Rumachenanck tribe|Rumachenanck]]), New York<ref name=g237/>\n***[[Kitchawank]] ([[Kichtawanks]], [[Kichtawank]]), New York<ref name=g237>Goddard 237</ref>\n***[[Minisink people|Minisink]], formerly New York<ref name=g72/>\n***[[Navasink]],<ref name=g237/> to the east along the north shore of New Jersey\n***[[Raritan people|Raritan]], formerly Westchester County, New York<ref name=g237/>\n***[[Sinsink people|Sinsink]] ([[Sintsink people|Sintsink]]), Westchester County, New York<ref name=g237/>\n***[[Siwanoy]], Massachusetts<ref name=g237/>\n***[[Tappan people|Tappan]], formerly New York<ref>Goddard 72, 237\u2013238</ref>\n***[[Waoranecks]]<ref name=g238>Goddard 238</ref>\n***[[Wappinger]] ([[Wecquaesgeek]], [[Nochpeem]]), formerly New York<ref name=\"ne198\"/><ref>Goddard 72 and 238</ref>\n***[[Warranawankongs]]<ref name=g238/>\n***[[Wiechquaeskeck]], formerly New York<ref name=g72/>\n**[[Delaware languages|Unami]]-speaking subgroups\n***[[Acquackanonk tribe|Acquackanonk]], Passaic River in northern New Jersey\n***[[Okehocking people|Okehocking]], southeast Pennsylvania<ref name=g238/>\n***[[Unalachtigo Lenape|Unalachtigo]], Delaware, New Jersey\n*[[Manahoac]], Virginia<ref name=s290>Sturtevant and Fogelson, 290</ref>\n*[[Mascouten]], formerly Michigan<ref name=ne_ix/>\n*[[Massachusett]], Massachusetts\n**[[Ponkapoag]], Massachusetts\n*[[Menominee]], Wisconsin<ref name=ne_ix/>\n*[[Mahican]] ([[Stockbridge Mahican]]<ref name=nmai/>) Connecticut, Massachusetts, New York, and Vermont<ref name=ne_ix/><ref name=\"ne198\"/>\n*[[Massachusett]], Massachusetts<ref name=nmai/><ref name=n161>Sturtevant and Trigger 161</ref>\n*[[Meherrin]], Virginia,<ref name=s293>Sturtevant and Fogelson, 293</ref> North Carolina\n*[[Mi'kmaq people|Mi'kmaq]] (Micmac), New Brunswick, Newfoundland and Labrador, Nova Scotia, Prince Edward Island, Quebec,<ref name=ne_ix/> and Maine\n* [[Mohegan]],<ref name=nmai/> Connecticut\n* [[Monacan people|Monacan]], Virginia<ref name=sf81/>\n* [[Montaukett]] ([[Montauk people|Montauk]]),<ref name=nmai/> New York\n* [[Monyton]] ([[Monetons]], Monekot, Moheton) ([[Siouan]]), West Virginia and Virginia\n* [[Nansemond]], Virginia\n* [[Nanticoke people|Nanticoke]], Delaware and Maryland<ref name=ne_ix/>\n**[[Accohannock]]\n* [[Narragansett people|Narragansett]], Rhode Island<ref name=nmai/>\n* [[Niantic people|Niantic]], coastal Connecticut<ref name=nmai/><ref name=n161/>\n* [[Nipmuc]] ([[Nipmuck]]), Connecticut, Massachusetts, and Rhode Island<ref name=n161/>\n* [[Nottaway]], Virginia,<ref name=s293/>\n* [[Occaneechi]] ([[Occaneechee]]), Virginia<ref name=s293/><ref name=s291>Sturtevant and Fogelson, 291</ref><ref>Sturtevant and Trigger 96</ref>\n*[[Passamaquoddy people|Passamaquoddy]], New Brunswick, and Maine<ref name=ne_ix/>\n*[[Patuxent people|Patuxent]], Maryland<ref name=n241/>\n*[[Paugusett people|Paugussett]], Connecticut<ref name=nmai/>\n**[[Potatuck]], New York<ref name=n161/>\n*[[Penobscot people|Penobscot]], Maine\n*[[Pequot]], Connecticut<ref name=nmai/>\n*[[Petun]] ([[Tionontate]]), Ontario<ref name=ne_ix/>\n*[[Piscataway tribe|Piscataway]], Maryland<ref name=n241/>\n*[[Pocumtuc]], western Massachusetts<ref name=n161/>\n* [[Podunk people|Podunk]], New York,<ref name=n161/> eastern Hartford County, Connecticut\n*[[Powhatan Confederacy]], Virginia<ref name=n241/>\n**[[Appomattoc]], Virginia\n**[[Arrohateck]], Virginia\n**[[Chesapeake people|Chesapeake]], Virginia\n**[[Chesepian]], Virginia\n**[[Chickahominy people|Chickahominy]], Virginia<ref name=\"s293\"/>\n**[[Kiskiack]], Virginia\n**[[Ma